## Partial Reloads (Refresh Only Some Props)

When you only want to reload part of the page data without a full Inertia visit:

```jsx
import { router } from '@inertiajs/react';

// Only reload 'products' prop from the controller
router.reload({ only: ['products'] });
```

---

## Event Handling

| React | Inertia + React |
|-------|-----------------|
| `<Link to="/path">` | `<Link href="/path">` |
| `<a href>` (full reload) | `<Link href>` (SPA nav) |
| `fetch POST` | `useForm().post(route(...))` |
| `fetch PUT/PATCH` | `useForm().put(route(...))` |
| `fetch DELETE` | `router.delete(route(...))` |
| Manual CSRF header | Handled automatically by Inertia |

