## Migration Checklist

- [ ] Install Inertia Laravel adapter: `composer require inertiajs/inertia-laravel:^3.0`
- [ ] Install Inertia React adapter: `npm install @inertiajs/react@^3`
- [ ] Optional: `npm install @inertiajs/vite@^3` and configure per [client-side setup](https://inertiajs.com/docs/v3/installation/client-side-setup.md)
- [ ] Replace `main.jsx` with Inertia bootstrap (`createInertiaApp`)
- [ ] Root Blade: add `@inertiaHead` / `@inertia` **or** `<x-inertia::head />` / `<x-inertia::app />` in `resources/views/app.blade.php` ([server-side setup](https://inertiajs.com/docs/v3/installation/server-side-setup.md)); then `php artisan view:clear`
- [ ] If upgrading from v2: republish `config/inertia.php` and merge customizations; replace `Inertia::lazy()` with `Inertia::optional()`
- [ ] Move page components from `src/pages/` to `resources/js/Pages/` (or your chosen folder that matches `resolve`)
- [ ] Remove React Router — replace with Inertia `<Link>` and `router.visit()`
- [ ] Replace all page-level `useEffect + fetch` with data from Laravel controller
- [ ] Replace `fetch POST` forms with `useForm` hook
- [ ] Replace `fetch PUT/DELETE` with `useForm().put()` / `router.delete()`
- [ ] Configure shared data (auth user, flash) in `HandleInertiaRequests` middleware
- [ ] Install Ziggy and use `route()` helper for named routes
- [ ] Add persistent layout to each page component
- [ ] Test back/forward browser navigation
- [ ] Test form validation error display
- [ ] Verify CSRF protection on all mutations

